# ── Stripe Test Mode Configuration ────────────────────────────────────────────
# This file contains test mode configuration for Stripe integration.
# Replace these values with your Stripe Dashboard test keys.
#
# HOW TO GET TEST KEYS:
# 1. Go to https://dashboard.stripe.com/register (create account if needed)
# 2. Toggle "Test mode" on (top-right switch)
# 3. Go to Developers → API keys
# 4. Copy "Secret key" (starts with sk_test_)
# 5. Copy "Publishable key" if needed for frontend (starts with pk_test_)
#
# HOW TO CREATE PRODUCTS & PRICES:
# 1. Go to Products → Add Product
# 2. Create "Pro Plan" with recurring pricing:
#    - $19.00/month USD
#    - ₹199.00/month INR
# 3. Create "Business Plan" with recurring pricing:
#    - $99.00/month USD
#    - ₹999.00/month INR
# 4. Copy the Price IDs (start with price_test_)
#
# HOW TO SETUP WEBHOOKS FOR LOCAL DEV:
# 1. Install Stripe CLI: winget install Stripe.stripe-cli
# 2. Run: stripe login
# 3. Run: stripe listen --forward-to http://localhost:3000/api/billing/webhook
# 4. Copy the webhook signing secret from the CLI output
# 5. OR use the provided script: powershell -File scripts\stripe-setup.ps1
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Stripe Test Keys ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_YOUR_SECRET_KEY_HERE
STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_test_YOUR_PUBLISHABLE_KEY_HERE

# ── Webhook Signing Secret ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
# From `stripe listen` CLI output or Stripe Dashboard webhook configuration
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_YOUR_WEBHOOK_SECRET_HERE

# ── Subscription Price IDs ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
# USD Prices (create in Stripe Dashboard → Products)
STRIPE_PRICE_PRO=price_test_pro_usd_HERE
STRIPE_PRICE_BUSINESS=price_test_business_usd_HERE

# INR Prices (create in Stripe Dashboard → Products)
STRIPE_PRICE_PRO_INR=price_test_pro_inr_HERE
STRIPE_PRICE_BUSINESS_INR=price_test_business_inr_HERE

# ── Test Cards (use these in Stripe Checkout test mode) ──────────────────────
# 4242 4242 4242 4242  → Successful payment
# 4000 0000 0000 9995  → Declined payment
# 4000 0025 0000 3155  → Requires 3D Secure authentication
# 4000 0000 0000 0002  → Always fails
# 4000 0000 0000 0010  → Requires attaching payment method

# ── Test Mode Checklist ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# [ ] 1. Create Stripe account (dashboard.stripe.com/register)
# [ ] 2. Get test secret key (sk_test_...)
# [ ] 3. Create Pro plan product with USD + INR prices
# [ ] 4. Create Business plan product with USD + INR prices
# [ ] 5. Update price IDs in this file
# [ ] 6. Install Stripe CLI (winget install Stripe.stripe-cli)
# [ ] 7. Login to CLI (stripe login)
# [ ] 8. Run webhook forwarding (scripts\stripe-setup.ps1)
# [ ] 9. Copy webhook secret (whsec_...) to this file
# [ ] 10. Run tests: node tests/stripe-api.test.mjs
# [ ] 11. Make a test purchase with card 4242 4242 4242 4242
# [ ] 12. Verify webhook events in Stripe Dashboard
